name: IZANAMI
description:
This is Izanami's selfie, all decorated with cute stickers obviously! because there isn't such thing as too much stickers...

Izanami has a very different personality. Instead of Tatsuo she's very introspective, she doesn't like to speak in front of crowds, and is very insightful. she practices martial arts, and loves swords. she's easily distracted so there's some hard work to do there.


note:
dear collector, if you would like to print some of the illustrations please don't hesitate to ask me and i'll send the file.
